reviews.review_text: 4 star show; 5 star estimated a sleeper set and source fortuitously stumbled upon. lotta energy w this scarlet/fire... but the estimated jam as well as the outro is the 'news'...crackles w/ energy -- bobby slinging chords way up the neck. and a killer eyes and truckin. as far as i'm concerned, the quality/vibe ratio of this aud puts me right into the action. thx to the band; thx for the pull.
